metadata.name: Concrete Jungle
metadata.description:
Once lived as a visual for the outstanding live shows of the producer, live act and DJ "INNELLEA", this masterpiece transforms into perpetual digital art, to give back the beloved community more than just dance, music and infinitive love.

This artwork is linked to the long awaited song "Concrete Jungle", which is a soundtrack of the three-part EP.

__
Transhumanism: The self-technicalization of Homo Faber is already in process and leads to the merging of the "Concrete Jungle" and the "False Reality" in all aspects of life. Will this process lead to a world where reality is relative?

What is reality? What should be reality?

__
By holding this NFT, you are empowered to enjoy the following benefits:

- UNIQUE 1/ 1 ARTWORK
- LIFELONG GUESTLIST (+1)
- MEET AND GREET
- INNELLEA SHIRT & WAIST BAG 
- PFP AIRDROP (NFT)
- PART OF INNELLEA FAMILY
__
Artwork by: ALEXANDER TRATTLER
